{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[null],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"footer":1,"image":1,"publicationDate":2,"active":3,"meta":4,"header":9,"url":10,"title":11,"lastUpdatedOn":12,"content":13,"scripts":1},"",1732233600000,true,{"title":5,"keywords":6,"description":7,"structured":1,"og":8},"About Genos: Leading the Way in Innovative Scientific Solutions for Research and Industry","Genos, scientific solutions, innovative research tools, commercial scientific solutions, research innovation, scientific discovery, advanced technologies, industry solutions, research and industry, scientific advancements","Learn about Genos, a pioneer in delivering innovative scientific solutions for research and industry. Discover how our advanced technologies are shaping the future of scientific discovery and commercial success.",{"image":1},"lpl-JSJH1cdNZHvn7Put3p4ZiF0K","/","Home","2025-03-28T13:10:09.355Z","\u003Cpb-navigation id=i93h labels=\"About,Publications,Services,Projects,Our team,Contact us\" links=/about,/publications,/services,/projects,/team,/contact>\u003C/pb-navigation>\u003Cpb-intro src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fhome%2Fgenos-bg.jpg?alt=media\" alt=Background id=CGyxEdzH7UAsvFuC content=asdfadsfž>\u003Cdiv id=i9f9fs class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=ia4pb3 class=gc-12>\u003Cpb-hero-content-landing id=iqyax9>\u003C/pb-hero-content-landing>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/pb-intro>\u003Cdiv id=yduVdji8B7ft9aSd class=\"grid grid-large analytics-hero spacer\">\u003Ccolumn id=vJGEFrIyYnbg60UF class=gc-12>\u003Ch1 id=tlbZvYJS1x0R6Cbq class=h3>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=B9DU0dSGJrPivlas>Simple and automated scientific solutions for your research or commercial needs.\u003C/span>\u003C/h1>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=9lVBcay3XSb3e4HB class=\"gc-3 gc-sm-6 gc-xs-6 analytic analytic-1\">\u003Ch2 id=yd5yjms1SHXDXgzi class=h4>\u003Cspan id=VT1Rrtf19V0Np3Fu class=analytic-number>200k+\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=w9DrGLGbPKUcMa6R class=analytic-text>Samples analyzed to date\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003Cdiv id=drJdtpxS5r2EAFQ9 class=analytic-bar>\u003C/div>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=kmf7FAAQ0VKhoE6J class=\"gc-3 gc-sm-6 gc-xs-6 analytic analytic-2\">\u003Ch2 id=GKTtxpTMLSw4I9BO class=h4>\u003Cspan id=zDomsbeC88vtkxMX class=analytic-number>500+\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=OcBhAWpzvBwx3BeF class=analytic-text>Samples analyzed daily\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003Cdiv id=H86bFF1Ywc4ohGMn class=analytic-bar>\u003C/div>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=QdL1OQXpbGPTnbGM class=\"gc-3 gc-sm-6 gc-xs-6 analytic analytic-3\">\u003Ch2 id=XJffutGfbl1MQKKE class=h4>\u003Cspan id=EjlIgvIfpHS5hy81 class=analytic-number>300+\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=7acE4rKv2icOqYwD class=analytic-text>Scientific publications\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003Cdiv id=YD5Fwd3K1e6GnW29 class=analytic-bar>\u003C/div>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=XMHc1fwjb8AlPRsF class=\"gc-3 gc-sm-6 gc-xs-6 analytic analytic-4\">\u003Ch2 id=TrcmYppFOPzGJED5 class=h4>\u003Cspan id=xNNI6pBxJvfwCyXP class=analytic-number>40+\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=FOK3JzlyHqehFmTS class=analytic-text>Collaboration projects\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003Cdiv id=uzl9D6gFYHsb2x3M class=analytic-bar>\u003C/div>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Cpb-labs id=igreg7 class=spacer>\u003C/pb-labs>\u003Csection id=aQa0yO9fLVK9G9lb class=\"complex-section world-class-scientists spacer\">\u003Cdiv id=ZB2ykMQUKha5m0fa class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=iCdmnOLVIRfKpf00 class=gc-9>\u003Ch2 id=HuaChmjvqno5aiel class=\"complex-section-title h3\">We are a team of leading experts in glycoscience, conducting \u003Ca href=\"\" id=ishxbj title=https://www.researchgate.net/institution/Genos-Ltd target=_blank>80%\u003C/a> of the global analyses in our lab.\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cpb-team id=iwpxiq>\u003C/pb-team>\u003Csection id=YA5FEVOEVWYCEXvO class=\"complex-section spacer\">\u003Cdiv id=99t12REcY3UdZDUw class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=MOMvkAGuSkXyzlxL class=gc-12>\u003Ch2 id=hs21csPYDrnEFdsG class=\"complex-section-title h3\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=i62tld>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan id=iysz38>Glycans \u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=ifkuy5>are the focus of our intense interest.\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=ol0BM2fqEy2TjSZV class=gc-8>\u003Cp id=iks9qc>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=is1rqf>Glycans are the ultimate layer of complexity of life. These complex oligosaccharides change the structure and function of proteins and other molecules.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>The level of molecular complexity achieved by glycosylation increases the proteome diversity to a level orders of magnitude greater than any other post-translational modification.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>Proteins depend on secondary modifications to maintain structural integrity and perform their fun-ction. Over half of all existing proteins are glycosylated, the average mass representation of the majority of proteins are glycans. All secreted proteins are glycosylated and can serve as biomarkers.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>Glycans are functional effectors in a variety of conditions, but also in autoimmune and chronic diseases. They are the biomarkers of inflammation and can prognose a variety of conditions.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Csection id=BRK1ENKU47gsqxHg class=complex-section>\u003Cdiv id=lu6RgyxszVN9fh9A class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=pZsfLecv3wkfHI0L class=gc-12>\u003Ch2 id=QTiVFd7WD6LgNXxH class=\"h2 complex-section-title\">\u003Cspan id=i9vwlq>The Human Glycome Project\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=ioig2x class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=igtfu7 class=\"gc-9 KYVq6mdbafW8YhmG gc-sm-12\">\u003Cp id=i4ixbk>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>An ambitious scientific initiative focused on mapping the entire human glycome, encompassing all glycans present in the human body.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>\u003Ca href=\"\" id=ipzu0e title=https://www.youtube.com/@HumanGlycomeProject/featured target=_blank>Watch the latest videos\u003C/a> on glycobiology research and innovations.\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cdiv id=i2fola class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=9MiFxV1VrUEEumpz class=\"gc-12 cta-arrows\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=dH3AJJky8RByCcRw class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=QD3k1YDaaQQXfefq class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=atl0rMWdgUhjtl89 class=arrow-big>\u003Ca id=ip6cuv href=https://human-glycome.org/ target=_blank class=hover-underline>human-glycome.org\u003C/a>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=panBLNlsTxXEQekC class=arrow-big>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=agSwYeDGfhqZ1wxS class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=QatGefcauW3QoQA3 class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Csection id=QxEoDGRj8XIIJmT7 class=complex-section>\u003Cdiv id=IGJLBSqkr2je3xQU class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid from-science-to-product\">\u003Ccolumn id=YeBbQQSOxfxUcTeR class=gc-9>\u003Ch2 id=Ki38WEjEwrTvDEj7 class=\"h2 complex-section-title from-science-to-product-title\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=iimqwr>From science to product: \u003Cspan>\u003Cspan id=izkexo>GlycanAge\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=J8mNKwmUc6gGtLJw class=gc-3>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fkit.png?alt=media\" id=uX0uQP8XAFtUyi7t class=\"complex-section-image from-science-to-product-img\">\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=csbWHQFtkslPAvTn class=\"gc-9 KYVq6mdbafW8YhmG gc-sm-10 gc-xs-12\">\u003Cp id=ilhfa8>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=i38duj>GlycanAge is a biological age testing kit (and a health improvement service). It does so through measuring number of pro and anti inflammatory glycans attached to IgG.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>It aims to help people increase the number of anti-inflammatory, and reduce number of pro-inflammatory glycans.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>Genos has researched glycans as a biomarker over the past 20 years, and now serves as the central hub for GlycanAge blood sample analysis.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cdiv id=i6imn1 class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=N8MJ9hXMJingWa75 class=\"gc-12 cta-arrows\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-green.svg?alt=media\" id=UhkdOwaoY92aluuj class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-green.svg?alt=media\" id=sgoMmtnawQ4Jdow5 class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-green.svg?alt=media\" id=BskE9ebAKRZ09QoK class=arrow-big>\u003Ca data-pblink id=gjiUJpY6sRTyfbQK href=https://glycanage.com/ >\u003C/a>\u003Ca id=ixv4is href=https://glycanage.com target=_blank>glycanage.com\u003C/a>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-green.svg?alt=media\" id=WLa2EKU7yBFuiDW0 class=arrow-big>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-green.svg?alt=media\" id=2hwekRwRk26wZ3BW class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-green.svg?alt=media\" id=comjYKTbjRRspgXM class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Csection id=KfoVnuoH7NAi5Bbw class=\"cta-request spacer\">\u003Cdiv id=sp9ylhyjgUxdJHqt class=\"grid grid-large cta-request-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=F4NIlDn4UW221qIw class=gc-12>\u003Ch2 id=HxCY39yasdbQWKRK class=\"cta-request-text h4\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=AxngyX2ddJSaizZs>If you’re interested in working with us or using our services, submit a request for free and we’ll schedule a meeting to discuss your ideas.\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=WFzUddwVChG803Ac class=gc-12>\u003Ca data-pblink id=mKXhMnZqmTOWRXbf href=/contact class=\"cta-big cta-yellow\">Get in touch\u003C/a>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cstyle>  #KYVq6mdbafW8YhmG{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#hs21csPYDrnEFdsG{color:black;max-width:20ch;}#i62tld{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#iysz38{color:#e58d19;}#is1rqf{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#i9vwlq{color:#4095bf;}#dH3AJJky8RByCcRw{color:black;}#iimqwr{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#izkexo{color:#80bf40;}#i38duj{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#UhkdOwaoY92aluuj{color:black;}#gjiUJpY6sRTyfbQK{color:black;}#N8MJ9hXMJingWa75{color:#4c8217;}#i6imn1{margin:5rem auto 0px auto;}#i2fola{margin:5rem auto 0px auto;}#ioig2x{margin:5rem auto 0px auto;}#ip6cuv{color:#175e82;}#CGyxEdzH7UAsvFuC{color:black;}#ifkuy5{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#QTiVFd7WD6LgNXxH{text-align:center;}#ishxbj{color:#80bf40;}#ipzu0e{color:#4094be;text-decoration:underline